	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The synonyms of the word &lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;pass&amp;eacute;&amp;#39;&lt;font color=&quot;#202124&quot;&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;are&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;antiquated, old, archaic,&amp;nbsp;obsolete,&amp;nbsp;unfashionable, old-fashioned&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The antonyms of the word &lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;pass&amp;eacute;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(32, 33, 36); &quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;are&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;current, modern, fashionable,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;accustomed&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;From the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;synonym&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;of the given word, we can say that the word&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;old-fashioned&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;is similar in meaning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;​Hence we can say that&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Old-fashioned​&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;is similar in meaning to the given word.&lt;/p&gt;
